00026 /* file_in_zip_read_info_s contain internal information about a file in zipfile,
00027     when reading and decompress it */
00028 typedef struct
00029 {
00030     CHAR  *read_buffer;            /* internal buffer for compressed data */
00031     z_stream stream;               /* zLib stream structure for inflate */
00032 
00033     UINT32 pos_in_zipfile;         /* position in byte on the zipfile, for fseek*/
00034     UINT32 stream_initialised;     /* flag set if stream structure is initialised*/
00035 
00036     UINT32 offset_local_extrafield;/* offset of the local extra field */
00037     UINT  size_local_extrafield;   /* size of the local extra field */
00038     UINT32 pos_local_extrafield;   /* position in the local extra field in read*/
00039 
00040     UINT32 crc32;                   /* crc32 of all data uncompressed */
00041     UINT32 crc32_wait;              /* crc32 we must obtain after decompress all */
00042     UINT32 rest_read_compressed;    /* number of byte to be decompressed */
00043     UINT32 rest_read_uncompressed;  /*number of byte to be obtained after decomp*/
00044 
00045     const CHAR* jar_file_name;
00046     FfsHandle jar_file_handle;
00047 
00048     UINT32 compression_method;      /* compression method (0==store) */
00049     UINT32 byte_before_the_zipfile; /* byte before the zipfile, (>0 for sfx)*/
00050 } FileInReadStatusInfo;
